{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-docs-page-jsx","path":"/docs/java/usage/generate-tests-with-plugin","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>To generate tests for Java code with UTBot plugin you must do the following steps:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Open your Java Project in IntelliJ IDEA and find a class you want to cover by unit tests:</li>\n</ol>\n<details>\n  <summary>\n    IDEA project\n  </summary>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/UnitTestBot/unittestbot.github.io/blob/source/resources/images/utbot-java/IDEA_Project.jpg\" alt=\"IDEA project\"></p>\n</details>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li><strong>Click to Alt + U</strong> - or - <strong>right mouse click</strong> on the file â†’ <strong>Generate tests with UtBot</strong>..:</li>\n</ol>\n<details>\n  <summary>\n    How to generate tests with plugin\n  </summary>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/UnitTestBot/unittestbot.github.io/blob/source/resources/images/utbot-java/IDEA_GeneratingTests.jpg\" alt=\"How to generate tests with plugin\"></p>\n</details>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>Select a method you'd like to cover by tests:</li>\n</ol>\n<details>\n  <summary>\n    How to choose method for unit test generation\n  </summary>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/UnitTestBot/unittestbot.github.io/blob/source/resources/images/utbot-java/ChooseMethodForUnitTestGeneration.jpg\" alt=\"How to choose method for unit tests generation\"></p>\n</details>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>Click <strong>OK</strong>:</li>\n</ol>\n<details>\n  <summary>\n    Generated tests\n  </summary>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/UnitTestBot/unittestbot.github.io/blob/source/resources/images/utbot-java/GeneratedTests.jpg\" alt=\"Generated tests\"></p>\n</details>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>That's is: tests are generated automatically w/o any additional actions from an user side</li>\n</ol>","frontmatter":{"path":"/docs/java/usage/generate-tests-with-plugin"}}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":["1550867996","2819311301"]}